{
  "stem": "15768.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And at the border from France to Spain, the German-- I guess at that point, they were SS really, not SR anymore-- did a body search.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "My mother and I were to put into one room and had a-- had to strip and had a very thorough body search for not smuggling anything out of the country.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at the end of it, I was still wearing some rubber boots that I was wearing because the weather was foul.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the SS man who was standing there with a whip, actually, confronted me across the room about I hadn't taken off my boots.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What was I hiding in them?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in a fit of fury, I kicked off the boot which was fairly loose on my foot.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it went flying across the room and just nearly hit him in the face.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother thought, oh, god.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is the end.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're not going to let us go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it took him a moment to get his composure.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then he smiled in a very sardonic kind of way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said, OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Doesn't make any difference anyway.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said, they're going to send you back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You'll be back here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You're not going to get out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we-- we-- the paper said OK.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so we got onto the-- the train through Spain, which was an old, rickety-rackety train with very sparse provisions, because we were going to be on the train a day and night and a day.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was raining.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we sat with the-- holding umbrellas, because the rain was coming through the roof of-- of the train.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, there was no relief from the weather.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's cold, damp.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were others.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I believe there were 10.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
